{"tid":291285,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"支爆危機：債務大山","createTime":"2017-06-20T12:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T01:46:43.000Z","uid":53223,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e055329b6f4e7c2c2e84976e757e7dd4cdc8236","tid":291285,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T12:33:16.000Z","msg":"中國國企的欠債達到了中國GDP的115%, 遠高於日本和韓國的欠債。日本和韓國的欠債只是GDP的30% 左右。<br />\n<br />\n國際信用評等機構穆迪投資者服務公司，24日突然宣布調降中國的信用評等，從原本的Aa3調降到A1，主要原因是中國債務不斷增加，經濟成長放緩，預期中國的經濟前景，可能會在未來幾年內惡化。<br />\n<br />\n穆迪在報告中指出，中國的經濟成長，可能在未來幾年放緩到5%左右，儘管中國政府將推出財政刺激政策，但衰退無法避免，而且中國的債務負擔，會在2018年快速提升到GDP的40%，並在未來5年內上升到45%。<br />\n<br />\n摩根大通的報告也顯示，<span style=\"color: red;\">中國的債務總額已達到去年GDP總值的253%，高於2013年的213%，和2008年的149%</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實都好得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e4fb7fc59b45c43e6212e948f3d5426c0eee4d","tid":291285,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T12:34:55.000Z","msg":"有冇高人講下爆起上黎香港會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f9179bc4145e4b9d6c954fee088a03de19451d","tid":291285,"uid":36482,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T12:35:33.000Z","msg":"有冇人記得支爆幾多年前開始講"},{"pid":"091615a0d705445a158e60019b498b8aeaaf9b09","tid":291285,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T12:37:20.000Z","msg":"其他有幾多%係中鐵？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fbd13fb52ca6371d4bfe668129f78a6f8cbe585","tid":291285,"uid":53619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T12:39:31.000Z","msg":"快啲搵地方跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bca4b2cffea5fe0c1339e488f28603598152b5f","tid":291285,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"